  <brief_title>Prognostic Value of Stem Cell Related Markers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prognostic Value of Stem Cell Related Markers CD24, CD44, CD326 and EPCR, for Predicting Breast Cancer Recurrence in Tumor Stages 0-II</official_title>
  <sponsors>
